[{"Code":"en","Title":"Monitoring transactions","Slug":"xenplatform-monitoring-transactions","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"4b4f7d68-5879-41f0-9c0e-4ca59422862e\"><img data-block-id=\"ae181fff-623b-4318-897a-2e6a6a3775d8\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/xp-step-3.webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"d4db0854-4af2-4fec-bb33-486c89d2e8a8\">You can monitor transactions in real-time and generate reports for all your accounts for reconciliation purposes.</p><ol data-block-id=\"84a728c8-c29b-4c6f-a855-93f39674c73c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"c8803270-e447-42d7-adea-aff40564f459\"><p data-block-id=\"ab668910-c0c6-47dc-9154-441af36ee506\">Log in to your Xendit dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"80ec379c-535a-4421-b03c-b8b46e4a8a27\"><p data-block-id=\"9007d0b2-86f9-44df-a84d-8eaea59bb576\">View a snapshot of your platform's payment volumes and performance over time</p></li><li data-block-id=\"022780cf-20d1-40ff-bd43-ddb513c73f45\"><p data-block-id=\"121ec1d2-8da0-4628-bcb1-c7c591484170\">Navigate to each sub-account and track their activities</p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"0b5a84d7-bb52-4656-817b-11cf3fef5c89\">Accounts overview</h2><p data-block-id=\"56e9406e-ca9e-4f28-b45f-25c511dac130\"><img data-block-id=\"c5f1c9d6-6716-4582-9f9c-6e1e091b8399\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/xp-accounts-new.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"e3659341-53b3-4ba0-b7b6-c5926af94cc2\">The Accounts Overview shows all the sub-accounts you created along with their status and current Cash Balances. By default it shows the most recently-created sub-accounts first, and you can filter the list by account status and date created. You can also search for sub-accounts by their business names, unique IDs, or business email.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"a155f16b-5882-48bc-bbf1-fc0f788b7775\">Account profile page</h2><ol data-block-id=\"16e656e2-f6c0-4800-874c-2e9bf0b9bfd7\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"f7fd2420-4818-44e7-a87f-64a5cb7e4efc\"><p data-block-id=\"3cc86253-27a2-4a33-b4c9-837e023736f1\">Navigate to the xenPlatform Accounts</p></li><li data-block-id=\"407392c1-3ec4-4b76-9027-bca173cc8722\"><p data-block-id=\"8c4b7b2f-5dd4-4563-be23-32f1f81e14f8\">Click on a specific sub-account to view more details</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"51070c84-a904-4be3-b6ac-f228cd2793ca\">The Account Profile Page shows basic information for the sub-account:</p><ul data-block-id=\"c0c9d902-b402-45b2-8572-577581664575\"><li data-block-id=\"ccb291a9-4af5-4ed2-a581-a3599e6a1789\"><p data-block-id=\"b9ac6b25-d069-4505-807f-20b9bb829352\">Name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"207b2ad9-3cb5-468c-a41b-7953713bfbf5\"><p data-block-id=\"fcc53d58-bc49-49b4-a30f-0c7a0398b567\">Email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"b47c0fb2-a6ee-40ec-aef6-8b4642eda376\"><p data-block-id=\"be7b31b9-1f5f-4d5e-8ef9-50ff4220593b\">Account ID</p></li><li data-block-id=\"670d23b3-3451-4d8e-99ee-84eb764b0dff\"><p data-block-id=\"5f575562-33e4-4623-ab2d-71f6c4c731d2\">Date Created</p></li><li data-block-id=\"e97c6204-081d-4e47-ad1a-412d6cf722bf\"><p data-block-id=\"92b302bf-41e8-4513-91f9-c8f32d76519b\">Account Status</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8b59656f-b47b-46b5-bd9b-3f6eeacc2910\"><p data-block-id=\"042d1b94-81b8-4937-84b2-5e8dfae4a192\">Account Type (Owned, Managed)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"fd71cc9e-d85b-4ebf-8b46-a9fa70907c13\"><p data-block-id=\"ebdbcab0-95f6-4a8a-866f-24b34def5e32\">Cash Balance</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d1f77da1-55b6-4329-8d47-718e8ad4e6d9\"><p data-block-id=\"521e4efb-0f85-4f88-80bc-48988f1ffb56\">Available Payment Channels</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"e6b11176-c25c-4b12-9482-53668cc57530\">Account Activity Page</h2><p data-block-id=\"2445442f-bc72-4376-ac1b-7a60f4d33ccb\">You can view the Balance and Transaction history for the sub-account your choose</p><ol data-block-id=\"e34ca3ca-d1e7-4475-b179-b710542aaf92\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"0749c102-4464-4917-877e-2d9721b506c4\"><p data-block-id=\"f7f8bdcf-dc06-4d4d-bd07-786d19e63339\">Navigate to the xenPlatform Accounts</p></li><li data-block-id=\"80bfaad5-e122-4130-aad1-3084995516f0\"><p data-block-id=\"c90e6b1b-bb04-49c6-984d-be25a1870050\">Click on more options for specific sub-account and select<strong> View Activity</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"fac4e2fd-29ff-4ae5-b8bf-b7ea9e7da7fa\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"1dc62f6e-ef9d-42eb-8414-c04aef181da7\"><p data-block-id=\"85ed6d60-0cf9-4551-915c-508c785c9a5c\">You can also switch to this tab from the Account Profile page</p></li></ol></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"20c80af9-ee7b-48ca-bf41-723e535e2506\">Monitoring via API</h2><p data-block-id=\"5e9313d4-dc00-44e0-93d8-bcac38614b2a\">You can also use your API key and utilize the following endpoints to retrieve and display information on your sub-accounts. Use the <code>for-user-id</code> header parameter to retrieve information for a sub-account.</p><pre data-block-id=\"3846be5b-e8c9-4cbc-b6c5-e46c4bc7c28a\" language=\"json\" data-custom-title=\"Custom\" class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\" spellcheck=\"false\">{\n  \"for-user-id\": \"my-sub-account-id-12345\"\n}</code></pre><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"876\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:876px;width:876px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:224px;\"><col style=\"width:310px;\"><col style=\"width:342px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"80532d0f-0031-4446-b1e1-3670e5959d05\">API</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"06ade9ff-8c84-4ea2-8762-8e274cb8e190\">Description</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"1930a518-e547-4ea3-8676-2d8a4b4f420c\">Use Case</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"fc1ddf08-985b-46e1-8bcf-d1d9415cf446\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/list-accounts\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Sub-accounts List</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"b8e89f83-cea8-4d88-b97e-37e722570c88\">Retrieves a list of sub-accounts</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"d37302ed-2670-4208-a9bd-8c17aaa38ea9\">Display a list of all sub-accounts in your application’s dashboard</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"1b7c2d3d-4778-4fa8-8648-798cb10f0dab\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-account\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Account</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"e9d1b7c0-dc9b-49e5-a574-e844be8ab59d\">Retrieves a sub-account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"a67135c1-e207-45c4-8308-d83cf41cf059\">Display detailed account information for one sub-account</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"fd81ac3b-679c-4117-a731-671430262a9f\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-balance\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Balance</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"33f43138-279d-41e4-8156-65af4bc141ab\">Displays the current balance for an account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"91ba5ad1-e6e0-46d0-8572-46b6295e379e\">Check the current live Balance for a sub-account</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"8045a230-137f-4d18-a815-02e3deaf5d10\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/list-transactions\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Transactions List</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"5e0a176a-ab3f-4834-94e1-b4344fac2f15\">Retrieves a list of transactions.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"c31e6a03-ff6e-4bb0-935c-478b63893f66\">Display recent transactions completed by a merchant</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"59d41517-bdf7-40d3-b4c2-d10376ae0e2e\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-transaction\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Transaction</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"b34400dc-ce06-43a1-8802-43a2b002ff58\">Retrieves a specific transaction</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"efb56357-87a4-4a7d-aebb-083ffa2bcb3f\">Check a specific transaction that was settled to a merchant</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"154a3d2b-197c-48d8-a878-7c518863699f\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/generate-report\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Generate Reports</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"03b133af-758c-4237-8993-dea6b2e7a519\">Generates a transaction or balance report</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"4fc7ee46-05aa-4236-996e-60ae67b682c3\">Monthly reconciliation </p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"d017060f-1aec-472f-a3db-4dc42dda14b9\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Monitoring transactions","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Lacak transaksi","Slug":"xenplatform-monitoring-transactions","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptu-1ewzst-029\"><img data-block-id=\"mcs1mptv-bzl4h8-030\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/xp-step-3.webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptv-b0xp0x-031\">Anda dapat memantau transaksi secara real-time dan membuat laporan untuk semua akun Anda untuk tujuan rekonsiliasi.</p><ol data-block-id=\"mcs1mptv-79p8yu-032\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptv-pkix44-033\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptv-ze0a5g-034\">Masuk ke dasbor Xendit Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptv-0yca1y-035\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptv-k40jeh-036\">Lihat cuplikan volume pembayaran dan performa platform Anda dari waktu ke waktu</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-dzkk9m-037\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-sbdzaq-038\">Klik setiap sub-akun dan lacak aktivitas mereka</p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-ag8cxa-039\">Overview sub-akun</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-2skeii-040\"><img data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-66xa5a-041\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/xp-accounts-new.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-kgm3ny-042\">Halaman Akun menunjukkan semua sub-akun yang Anda buat bersama dengan status dan Saldo saat ini. Secara default, ini menampilkan sub-akun yang paling baru dibuat terlebih dahulu, dan Anda dapat memfilter daftar berdasarkan status akun dan tanggal pembuatan. Anda juga dapat mencari sub-akun berdasarkan nama bisnis, ID unik, atau email bisnisnya.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-hkji5l-043\">Halaman profil akun</h2><ol data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-wl8bjx-044\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-omk6cn-045\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-ksvtmw-046\">Buka halaman Akun xenPlatform</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-pybyfy-047\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-hcun84-048\">Klik sub-akun tertentu untuk melihat detail lebih lanjut.</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-6448c0-049\">Halaman Profil Akun menampilkan informasi dasar untuk sub-akun:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-z9ev2i-050\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-li06n4-051\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-ljxmef-052\">Nama</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-idiiuu-053\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-uysrhm-054\">Email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-6wvzw8-055\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-2sb1f4-056\">ID Akun</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-ew01y3-057\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-jstiqp-058\">Tanggal Dibuat</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-lw4dbg-059\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-ilc1as-060\">Status Akun</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-zhfi8g-061\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-48t5n9-062\">Jenis Akun (Owned, Managed)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-bnwfbh-063\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptw-6pmsoh-064\">Saldo</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-se4ht5-065\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-6hck1r-066\">Channel Pembayaran yang Tersedia</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-r1dbmt-067\">Halaman aktivitas sub-akun</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-x68n9b-068\">Anda dapat melihat Riwayat Saldo dan Transaksi untuk sub-akun yang Anda pilih</p><ol data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-bi9ctx-069\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-utgpm0-070\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-coii29-071\">Buka Akun xenPlatform</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-o49uev-072\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-n27t7s-073\">Klik opsi lainnya untuk sub-akun tertentu dan pilih <strong>Lihat Aktivitas</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-u05hv1-074\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-nr7cg6-075\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-50sjcc-076\">Anda juga dapat beralih ke tab ini dari halaman Profil Akun</p></li></ol></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-zbzxsn-077\">Pemantauan melalui API</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-u21qgn-078\">Anda juga dapat menggunakan API key dan menggunakan endpoint berikut untuk mengambil dan menampilkan informasi pada sub-akun Anda. Gunakan parameter header <code>for-user-id</code> untuk mengambil informasi sub-akun.</p><pre data-block-id=\"mcs1mptx-t9fr1e-079\" language=\"json\" data-custom-title=\"Custom\" class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\" spellcheck=\"false\">{\n  \"for-user-id\": \"my-sub-account-id-12345\"\n}</code></pre><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"876\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:876px;width:876px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:224px;\"><col style=\"width:310px;\"><col style=\"width:342px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptz-dk45rs-080\">API</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptz-92fxcv-081\">Deskripsi</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptz-brt4s8-082\">Kasus penggunaan</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptz-1gcgc2-083\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/list-accounts\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Sub-accounts List</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptz-hp2bfy-084\">Mengambil daftar sub-akun</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mptz-bprqxy-085\">Menampilkan daftar semua sub-akun di dasbor aplikasi Anda</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu0-ks40vt-086\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-account\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Account</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu0-0jowc4-087\">Mengambil sub-akun</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu0-ewc1kj-088\">Menampilkan informasi akun terperinci untuk satu sub-akun</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu0-1culol-089\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-balances\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Balance</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu0-zpj6mf-090\">Menampilkan saldo saat ini untuk akun</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu0-2wcpwt-091\">Cek Saldo langsung saat ini untuk sub-akun</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu1-skz8pp-092\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/list-transactions\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Transactions List</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu1-87pgtn-093\">Mengambil daftar transaksi.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu1-up1pww-094\">Menampilkan transaksi terbaru yang diselesaikan oleh merchant</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu1-zdnlk5-095\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-transaction\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Transaction</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu1-jlyh1u-096\">Mengambil transaksi tertentu</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu1-8be9ht-097\">Memeriksa transaksi tertentu yang diselesaikan ke merchant</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu2-m1rjpc-098\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/generate-report\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Generate Reports</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu2-81e7jg-099\">Menghasilkan laporan transaksi atau saldo</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu2-qr958j-100\">Rekonsiliasi bulanan </p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mcs1mpu2-mcwjyy-101\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Lacak transaksi","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"การตรวจสอบธุรกรรม","Slug":"real-time-transactions","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"4b4f7d68-5879-41f0-9c0e-4ca59422862e\"><img data-block-id=\"ae181fff-623b-4318-897a-2e6a6a3775d8\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/xp-step-3.webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"d4db0854-4af2-4fec-bb33-486c89d2e8a8\">คุณสามารถติดตามธุรกรรมแบบ real-time และสร้างรายงานสำหรับบัญชีทั้งหมดของคุณเพื่อวัตถุประสงค์ในการทำ reconciliation</p><ol data-block-id=\"84a728c8-c29b-4c6f-a855-93f39674c73c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"c8803270-e447-42d7-adea-aff40564f459\"><p data-block-id=\"ab668910-c0c6-47dc-9154-441af36ee506\">เข้าสู่ระบบ Xendit dashboard ของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"80ec379c-535a-4421-b03c-b8b46e4a8a27\"><p data-block-id=\"9007d0b2-86f9-44df-a84d-8eaea59bb576\">ดูภาพรวมของปริมาณการชำระเงิน (payment volumes) และประสิทธิภาพของ platform ของคุณในช่วงเวลาที่ผ่านมา</p></li><li data-block-id=\"022780cf-20d1-40ff-bd43-ddb513c73f45\"><p data-block-id=\"121ec1d2-8da0-4628-bcb1-c7c591484170\">ไปที่ sub-account แต่ละบัญชีและติดตามกิจกรรมของบัญชีเหล่านั้น</p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"0b5a84d7-bb52-4656-817b-11cf3fef5c89\">Accounts overview</h2><p data-block-id=\"56e9406e-ca9e-4f28-b45f-25c511dac130\"><img data-block-id=\"c5f1c9d6-6716-4582-9f9c-6e1e091b8399\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/xp-accounts-new.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"e3659341-53b3-4ba0-b7b6-c5926af94cc2\">Accounts Overview แสดง sub-accounts ทั้งหมดที่คุณสร้างขึ้น พร้อมด้วย status และ Cash Balances ปัจจุบัน โดยค่าเริ่มต้นจะแสดง sub-accounts ที่สร้างล่าสุดก่อน และคุณสามารถกรองรายการตาม account status และ date created ได้ คุณยังสามารถค้นหา sub-accounts ตามชื่อธุรกิจ, unique IDs, หรือ business email ได้อีกด้วย</p><h2 data-block-id=\"a155f16b-5882-48bc-bbf1-fc0f788b7775\">Account profile page</h2><ol data-block-id=\"16e656e2-f6c0-4800-874c-2e9bf0b9bfd7\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"f7fd2420-4818-44e7-a87f-64a5cb7e4efc\"><p data-block-id=\"3cc86253-27a2-4a33-b4c9-837e023736f1\">ไปที่ xenPlatform Accounts</p></li><li data-block-id=\"407392c1-3ec4-4b76-9027-bca173cc8722\"><p data-block-id=\"8c4b7b2f-5dd4-4563-be23-32f1f81e14f8\">คลิกที่ sub-account ที่ต้องการเพื่อดูรายละเอียดเพิ่มเติม</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"51070c84-a904-4be3-b6ac-f228cd2793ca\">Account Profile Page แสดงข้อมูลพื้นฐานสำหรับ sub-account:</p><ul data-block-id=\"c0c9d902-b402-45b2-8572-577581664575\"><li data-block-id=\"ccb291a9-4af5-4ed2-a581-a3599e6a1789\"><p data-block-id=\"b9ac6b25-d069-4505-807f-20b9bb829352\">ชื่อ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"207b2ad9-3cb5-468c-a41b-79853713bfbf5\"><p data-block-id=\"fcc53d58-bc49-49b4-a30f-0c7a0398b567\">Email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"b47c0fb2-a6ee-40ec-aef6-8b4642eda376\"><p data-block-id=\"be7b31b9-1f5f-4d5e-8ef9-50ff4220593b\">Account ID</p></li><li data-block-id=\"670d23b3-3451-4d8e-99ee-84eb764b0dff\"><p data-block-id=\"5f575562-33e4-4623-ab2d-71f6c4c731d2\">Date Created</p></li><li data-block-id=\"e97c6204-081d-4e47-ad1a-412d6cf722bf\"><p data-block-id=\"92b302bf-41e8-4513-91f9-c8f32d76519b\">Account Status</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8b59656f-b47b-46b5-bd9b-3f6eeacc2910\"><p data-block-id=\"042d1b94-81b8-4937-84b2-5e8dfae4a192\">Account Type (Owned, Managed)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"fd71cc9e-d85b-4ebf-8b46-a9fa70907c13\"><p data-block-id=\"ebdbcab0-95f6-4a8a-866f-24b34def5e32\">Cash Balance</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d1f77da1-55b6-4329-8d47-718e8ad4e6d9\"><p data-block-id=\"521e4efb-0f85-4f88-80bc-48988f1ffb56\">Available Payment Channels</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"e6b11176-c25c-4b12-9482-53668cc57530\">Account Activity Page</h2><p data-block-id=\"2445442f-bc72-4376-ac1b-7a60f4d33ccb\">คุณสามารถดู Balance และ Transaction history สำหรับ sub-account ที่คุณเลือกได้</p><ol data-block-id=\"e34ca3ca-d1e7-4475-b179-b710542aaf92\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"0749c102-4464-4917-877e-2d9721b506c4\"><p data-block-id=\"f7f8bdcf-dc06-4d4d-bd07-786d19e63339\">ไปที่ xenPlatform Accounts</p></li><li data-block-id=\"80bfaad5-e122-4130-aad1-3084995516f0\"><p data-block-id=\"c90e6b1b-bb04-49c6-984d-be25a1870050\">คลิกที่ตัวเลือกเพิ่มเติมสำหรับ sub-account ที่ต้องการ และเลือก<strong> View Activity</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"fac4e2fd-29ff-4ae5-b8bf-b7ea9e7da7fa\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"1dc62f6e-ef9d-42eb-8414-c04aef181da7\"><p data-block-id=\"85ed6d60-0cf9-4551-915c-508c785c9a5c\">คุณยังสามารถเปลี่ยนไปที่แท็บนี้ได้จาก Account Profile page</p></li></ol></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"20c80af9-ee7b-48ca-bf41-723e535e2506\">Monitoring via API</h2><p data-block-id=\"5e9313d4-dc00-44e0-93d8-bcac38614b2a\">คุณยังสามารถใช้ API key ของคุณและใช้ endpoints ต่อไปนี้เพื่อดึงและแสดงข้อมูลเกี่ยวกับ sub-accounts ของคุณ ใช้ header parameter <code>for-user-id</code> เพื่อดึงข้อมูลสำหรับ sub-account</p><pre data-block-id=\"3846be5b-e8c9-4cbc-b6c5-e46c4bc7c28a\" language=\"json\" data-custom-title=\"Custom\" class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\" spellcheck=\"false\">{\n  &quot;for-user-id&quot;: &quot;my-sub-account-id-12345&quot;\n}</code></pre><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"876\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:876px;width:876px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:224px;\"><col style=\"width:310px;\"><col style=\"width:342px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"80532d0f-0031-4446-b1e1-3670e5959d05\">API</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"06ade9ff-8c84-4ea2-8762-8e274cb8e190\">คำอธิบาย</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"1930a518-e547-4ea3-8676-2d8a4b4f420c\">กรณีการใช้งาน</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"fc1ddf08-985b-46e1-8bcf-d1d9415cf446\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/list-accounts\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Sub-accounts List</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"b8e89f83-cea8-4d88-b97e-37e722570c88\">ดึงรายการ sub-accounts</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"d37302ed-2670-4208-a9bd-8c17aaa38ea9\">แสดงรายการ sub-accounts ทั้งหมดใน dashboard ของแอปพลิเคชันของคุณ</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"1b7c2d3d-4778-4fa8-8648-798cb10f0dab\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-account\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Account</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"e9d1b7c0-dc9b-49e5-a574-e844be8ab59d\">ดึง sub-account</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"a67135c1-e207-45c4-8308-d83cf41cf059\">แสดงข้อมูลบัญชีโดยละเอียดสำหรับ sub-account หนึ่งบัญชี</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"fd81ac3b-679c-4117-a731-671430262a9f\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-balance\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Balance</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"33f43138-279d-41e4-8156-65af4bc141ab\">แสดงยอด balance ปัจจุบันสำหรับบัญชี</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"91ba5ad1-e6e0-46d0-8572-46b6295e379e\">ตรวจสอบ Live Balance ปัจจุบันสำหรับ sub-account</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"8045a230-137f-4d18-a815-02e3deaf5d10\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/list-transactions\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Transactions List</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"5e0a176a-ab3f-4834-94e1-b4344fac2f15\">ดึงรายการ transactions</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"c31e6a03-ff6e-4bb0-935c-478b63893f66\">แสดง transactions ล่าสุดที่ดำเนินการโดย merchant</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"59d41517-bdf7-40d3-b4c2-d10376ae0e2e\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-transaction\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Transaction</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"b34400dc-ce06-43a1-8802-43a2b002ff58\">ดึง transaction ที่เฉพาะเจาะจง</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"efb56357-87a4-4a7d-aebb-083ffa2bcb3f\">ตรวจสอบ transaction ที่เฉพาะเจาะจงซึ่งได้รับการชำระไปยัง merchant</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"154a3d2b-197c-48d8-a878-7c518863699f\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/generate-report\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Generate Reports</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"03b133af-758c-4237-8993-dea6b2e7a519\">สร้างรายงาน transaction หรือ balance</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"4fc7ee46-05aa-4236-996e-60ae67b682c3\">Monthly reconciliation </p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"d017060f-1aec-472f-a3db-4dc42dda14b9\"></p>","SeoTitle":"การตรวจสอบธุรกรรม","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Monitoreo de transacciones","Slug":"xenplatform-monitoring-transactions","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"4b4f7d68-5879-41f0-9c0e-4ca59422862e\"><img data-block-id=\"ae181fff-623b-4318-897a-2e6a6a3775d8\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/xp-step-3.webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"d4db0854-4af2-4fec-bb33-486c89d2e8a8\">Usted puede monitorear transacciones en tiempo real y generar reportes para todas sus cuentas con fines de conciliación.</p><ol data-block-id=\"84a728c8-c29b-4c6f-a855-93f39674c73c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"c8803270-e447-42d7-adea-aff40564f459\"><p data-block-id=\"ab668910-c0c6-47dc-9154-441af36ee506\">Inicie sesión en su dashboard de Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"80ec379c-535a-4421-b03c-b8b46e4a8a27\"><p data-block-id=\"9007d0b2-86f9-44df-a84d-8eaea59bb576\">Vea un resumen de los volúmenes de Payment y el rendimiento de su plataforma a lo largo del tiempo</p></li><li data-block-id=\"022780cf-20d1-40ff-bd43-ddb513c73f45\"><p data-block-id=\"121ec1d2-8da0-4628-bcb1-c7c591484170\">Navegue a cada sub-cuenta y rastree sus actividades</p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"0b5a84d7-bb52-4656-817b-11cf3fef5c89\">Cuentas: resumen general</h2><p data-block-id=\"56e9406e-ca9e-4f28-b45f-25c511dac130\"><img data-block-id=\"c5f1c9d6-6716-4582-9f9c-6e1e091b8399\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/xp-accounts-new.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"e3659341-53b3-4ba0-b7b6-c5926af94cc2\">El Resumen General de Cuentas muestra todas las sub-cuentas que usted creó junto con su estado y Saldos de Efectivo (Cash Balances) actuales. Por defecto, muestra primero las sub-cuentas creadas más recientemente, y usted puede filtrar la lista por estado de cuenta y fecha de creación. También puede buscar sub-cuentas por sus nombres comerciales, ID únicos o correo electrónico comercial.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"a155f16b-5882-48bc-bbf1-fc0f788b7775\">Página de perfil de Cuenta</h2><ol data-block-id=\"16e656e2-f6c0-4800-874c-2e9bf0b9bfd7\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"f7fd2420-4818-44e7-a87f-64a5cb7e4efc\"><p data-block-id=\"3cc86253-27a2-4a33-b4c9-837e023736f1\">Navegue a Cuentas de xenPlatform</p></li><li data-block-id=\"407392c1-3ec4-4b76-9027-bca173cc8722\"><p data-block-id=\"8c4b7b2f-5dd4-4563-be23-32f1f81e14f8\">Haga clic en una sub-cuenta específica para ver más detalles</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"51070c84-a904-4be3-b6ac-f228cd2793ca\">La Página de Perfil de Cuenta muestra información básica de la sub-cuenta:</p><ul data-block-id=\"c0c9d902-b402-45b2-8572-577581664575\"><li data-block-id=\"ccb291a9-4af5-4ed2-a581-a3599e6a1789\"><p data-block-id=\"b9ac6b25-d069-4505-807f-20b9bb829352\">Nombre</p></li><li data-block-id=\"207b2ad9-3cb5-468c-a41b-7953713bfbf5\"><p data-block-id=\"fcc53d58-bc49-49b4-a30f-0c7a0398b567\">Correo electrónico</p></li><li data-block-id=\"b47c0fb2-a6ee-40ec-aef6-8b4642eda376\"><p data-block-id=\"be7b31b9-1f5f-4d5e-8ef9-50ff4220593b\">ID de Cuenta</p></li><li data-block-id=\"670d23b3-3451-4d8e-99ee-84eb764b0dff\"><p data-block-id=\"5f575562-33e4-4623-ab2d-71f6c4c731d2\">Fecha de Creación</p></li><li data-block-id=\"e97c6204-081d-4e47-ad1a-412d6cf722bf\"><p data-block-id=\"92b302bf-41e8-4513-91f9-c8f32d76519b\">Estado de Cuenta</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8b59656f-b47b-46b5-bd9b-3f6eeacc2910\"><p data-block-id=\"042d1b94-81b8-4937-84b2-5e8dfae4a192\">Tipo de Cuenta (Owned, Managed)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"fd71cc9e-d85b-4ebf-8b46-a9fa70907c13\"><p data-block-id=\"ebdbcab0-95f6-4a8a-866f-24b34def5e32\">Saldo de Efectivo</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d1f77da1-55b6-4329-8d47-718e8ad4e6d9\"><p data-block-id=\"521e4efb-0f85-4f88-80bc-48988f1ffb56\">Canales de Pago Disponibles</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"e6b11176-c25c-4b12-9482-53668cc57530\">Página de Actividad de Cuenta</h2><p data-block-id=\"2445442f-bc72-4376-ac1b-7a60f4d33ccb\">Usted puede ver el historial de Saldo y Transacciones de la sub-cuenta que elija</p><ol data-block-id=\"e34ca3ca-d1e7-4475-b179-b710542aaf92\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"0749c102-4464-4917-877e-2d9721b506c4\"><p data-block-id=\"f7f8bdcf-dc06-4d4d-bd07-786d19e63339\">Navegue a Cuentas de xenPlatform</p></li><li data-block-id=\"80bfaad5-e122-4130-aad1-3084995516f0\"><p data-block-id=\"c90e6b1b-bb04-49c6-984d-be25a1870050\">Haga clic en más opciones para una sub-cuenta específica y seleccione<strong> View Activity</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"fac4e2fd-29ff-4ae5-b8bf-b7ea9e7da7fa\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"1dc62f6e-ef9d-42eb-8414-c04aef181da7\"><p data-block-id=\"85ed6d60-0cf9-4551-915c-508c785c9a5c\">También puede cambiar a esta pestaña desde la página de Perfil de Cuenta</p></li></ol></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"20c80af9-ee7b-48ca-bf41-723e535e2506\">Monitoreo a través de API</h2><p data-block-id=\"5e9313d4-dc00-44e0-93d8-bcac38614b2a\">Usted también puede usar su API key y utilizar los siguientes endpoints para obtener y mostrar información sobre sus sub-cuentas. Use el parámetro header <code>for-user-id</code> para obtener información de una sub-cuenta.</p><pre data-block-id=\"3846be5b-e8c9-4cbc-b6c5-e46c4bc7c28a\" language=\"json\" data-custom-title=\"Personalizado\" class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\" spellcheck=\"false\">{\n  &quot;for-user-id&quot;: &quot;my-sub-account-id-12345&quot;\n}</code></pre><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"876\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:876px;width:876px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:224px;\"><col style=\"width:310px;\"><col style=\"width:342px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"80532d0f-0031-4446-b1e1-3670e5959d05\">API</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"06ade9ff-8c84-4ea2-8762-8e274cb8e190\">Descripción</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"1930a518-e547-4ea3-8676-2d8a4b4f420c\">Caso de Uso</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"fc1ddf08-985b-46e1-8bcf-d1d9415cf446\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/list-accounts\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Sub-accounts List</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"b8e89f83-cea8-4d88-b97e-37e722570c88\">Obtiene una lista de sub-cuentas</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"d37302ed-2670-4208-a9bd-8c17aaa38ea9\">Muestre una lista de todas las sub-cuentas en el dashboard de su aplicación</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"1b7c2d3d-4778-4fa8-8648-798cb10f0dab\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-account\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Account</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"e9d1b7c0-dc9b-49e5-a574-e844be8ab59d\">Obtiene una sub-cuenta</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"a67135c1-e207-45c4-8308-d83cf41cf059\">Muestre información detallada de una sub-cuenta</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"fd81ac3b-679c-4117-a731-671430262a9f\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-balance\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Balance</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"33f43138-279d-41e4-8156-65af4bc141ab\">Muestra el saldo actual de una cuenta</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"91ba5ad1-e6e0-46d0-8572-46b6295e379e\">Verifique el Saldo (Balance) actual en vivo de una sub-cuenta</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"8045a230-137f-4d18-a815-02e3deaf5d10\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/list-transactions\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Transactions List</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"5e0a176a-ab3f-4834-94e1-b4344fac2f15\">Obtiene una lista de transacciones.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"c31e6a03-ff6e-4bb0-935c-478b63893f66\">Muestre las transacciones recientes completadas por un comercio</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"59d41517-bdf7-40d3-b4c2-d10376ae0e2e\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/get-transaction\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">GET Transaction</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"b34400dc-ce06-43a1-8802-43a2b002ff58\">Obtiene una transacción específica</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"efb56357-87a4-4a7d-aebb-083ffa2bcb3f\">Verifique una transacción específica que fue liquidada a un comercio</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"224\"><p data-block-id=\"154a3d2b-197c-48d8-a878-7c518863699f\"><a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/apidocs/generate-report\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Generate Reports</a></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"310\"><p data-block-id=\"03b133af-758c-4237-8993-dea6b2e7a519\">Genera un reporte de transacciones o saldo</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"342\"><p data-block-id=\"4fc7ee46-05aa-4236-996e-60ae67b682c3\">Conciliación mensual </p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"d017060f-1aec-472f-a3db-4dc42dda14b9\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Monitoreo de transacciones","Description":null}]